description: Thena and Kro's children become targets of the Deviants. It becomes a race against time as the Eternals rush to rescue them.
name: The Herod Factor

description:
The Death of Superman
The Man of Steel pays the ultimate price for defending his beloved adopted city, Metropolis.
Who was Doomsday?
The Monster who killed Superman and thousands of others was himself destroyed, but the mystery continues. Who was he? Where did he come from?
The Justice League of America Carries On
Defeated by Doomsday, they now must face the future with the loss of their greatest ally. What lies ahead?
The World Reacts
Fellow super-heroes, along with world leaders and cultural figures, reflect upon the loss of Earth's greatest hero.
name: The Life and Death of The Man of Steel

description: The most anticipated series of 2010 is here! Superstar writer Grant Morrison tackles his most ambitious project to date with THE RETURN OF BRUCE WAYNE, a special six-part series that chronicles the return of the original man behind Batman's cape and cowl! Each issue spans a different era of time and features the dynamic artwork of one of today's artistic juggernauts, starting with Chris Sprouse (TOM STRONG) on the extra-sized issue #1 and Frazer Irving (SEVEN SOLDIERS: KLARION) on the 40-page issue #2!
name: Until the End of Time

volume.name: Batman: The Return of Bruce Wayne
